Add option to config.m4 to -rpath path to ffmpeg libs
Add check for system GD library and/or bundled GD library to config.m4

new getFrame symantics
   noarg getFrame gets the next frame from a movie or if the video stream 
   isn't opened then opens codec and retrives the first frame

   onearg getFrame opens codecs if they're not opened and gets the frame 
   specified in the parameter
